name: The Orb of Protection - Galactibles™ #20
description: Holy Balls of Light! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #20,  the “Orb of Protection!” Collecting this little blue ball of energy not only lights your way as you creep through the Galactiverse but also provides valuable protection with an impenetrable forcefield! Your Mana has been raised by +1,000,000 bits! Custom music made by Pyramid Guy! Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2021 | galactibles.com
